                Want to feature the McGennis family story? Interested in interviewing us about entrepreneurship
                in Jefferson City? Reach out through our social media.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="group bg-white p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-mcgennis-forest">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2 tracking-tight">
